title: #92Noon! Florio/SnobGame/Zimmer/Guerin/Leo/Ron&Gabe
description: Full show! Florio out of the starting gate, Stump the Snob, Zimmer press conference, Wild GM Bill Guerin, Jordan Leopold catchup, then VEN's Gabe Henderson and Ron Johnson both join for Vikings opinions to wrap the show!
